 class GuiPanelMyproxyReg
extends GuiPanelGeneric
implements java.awt.event.ActionListener

This class is the Register with GRIDportal pane. It is a gui form which allows a certificate to be registered with MyProxy, later to be use when logging into GRIDportal.

Author:
Martin Matusiak
